  &lt;li&gt;The code above has an extra space between &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;%&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;}&lt;/code&gt; to avoid my Jekyll trying to parse it…&lt;/li&gt;
